This is a mirror + patches of Google's PDFium project

It contains the following changes:

  * Is built as a shared library
  * Does not depend on V8
  * Has debian build configuration

Ruby Bindings for the library are available at:
https://github.com/nathanstitt/pdfium-ruby

An Ubuntu PPA containing compiled version of this repository: 
https://launchpad.net/~nathan-stitt/+archive/ubuntu/pdfium

The official home for PDFium is located at: https://code.google.com/p/pdfium/wiki/Build
